-- Puerto Rico weighs on Templeton funds muni bond business
-- 
-- Wed Jul 30, 2014 10:46AM EDT
-- None



July 30 (Reuters) - Franklin Resources Inc <BEN.N> Chief Executive Gregory Johnson said Wednesday that investors made net withdrawals of $400 million from the company's Templeton municipal bond funds during the fiscal third quarter, a trend that may continue in the short term as they fret over Puerto Rico's chronic fiscal woes.

